    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚总统部署军队制止“叛国”抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/kenyan-president-deploys-military-to-halt-treasonous-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托对全国范围内的反政府抗议活动进行反击，此次抗议活动造成至少五人死亡，他称其为“叛国行为”，并派遣军队结束骚乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/kenyan-president-deploys-military-to-halt-treasonous-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:59:12 GMT</pubDate>
